<div id="SizeChartModal" class="size-chart-modal">
  <div class="size-chart-overlay"></div>
  <div class="size-chart-content" style="background-color: {{ bg_color }}; color: {{ text_color }};">
    <button type="button" class="close-modal">&times;</button>
    <h2 style="font-size: {{ font_size | plus: 4 }}px; font-weight: {{ font_weight }};">Size Chart</h2>
    <div class="table-wrapper">
      <table
        class="size-chart-table"
        style="font-size: {{ font_size }}px; font-weight: {{ font_weight }}; border-color: {{ text_color }};"
      >
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Women</th>
            <th>Small</th>
            <th>Medium</th>
            <th>Large</th>
            <th>X-large</th>
            <th>XX-Large</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>Neck</td>
            <td>14-14.5</td>
            <td>15-15.5</td>
            <td>16-16.5</td>
            <td>17-17.5</td>
            <td>18-18.5</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Chest</td>
            <td>35-37</td>
            <td>38-40</td>
            <td>41-43</td>
            <td>44-46</td>
            <td>47-49</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Sleeve</td>
            <td>32-33</td>
            <td>33-34</td>
            <td>34-35</td>
            <td>35-36</td>
            <td>36-36.5</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Waist</td>
            <td>29-32</td>
            <td>22-34</td>
            <td>35-37</td>
            <td>38-40</td>
            <td>41-43</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
    <div class="size-chart-footer" style="font-size: {{ font_size | minus: 2 }}px;">
      <p>
        <strong>Neck:</strong> Measure around the middle of your neck (at the Adam's apple), keeping the tape a bit
        loose.
      </p>
      <p><strong>Chest:</strong> Measure under your arms around the fullest part of your chest.</p>
      <p>
        <strong>Arm length:</strong> Bend your elbow 90 degrees and place your hand on your hip. Hold the tape at the
        center of the back of your neck. Measure across your shoulder to your elbow and down to your wrist. The total
        length is your sleeve length.
      </p>
      <p><strong>Waist:</strong> Measure around your natural waistline, keeping the tape a bit loose.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
